data.description: Beautiful Turn Key Pulte Home...Ready for a New Owner Today!  Stay Cozy with Dual Heater/AC Units Plus A Gas Fireplace Too...Winter is Coming Stay Warm!  Gourmet Kitchen with Nice Lighting, SS Appliances and Tons of Cabinet/Counter Space...Perfect for The Holidays!  Enormous Living Area with Plush New Carpeting, Soaring Ceilings, T/V Mount and Modern Remote Ceiling Fan/Light!  New Flooring Flows into Separate Dining Rm with No Details Missed Including Deco-Wood Paneling, French Doors and Chandelier!  Private Owners Suite Won't Go Un-Noticed with Bay Window Design, High Ceilings and Updated Remote Ceiling/Light!  Primary Bath Fit For Any King/Queen with Wall to Wall Mirror, Over-Sized Vanity Including Dual Sinks, Separate Shower/Tub and a Huge Walk-In Closet!  Upstairs You'll Find a Bonus Rm...Perfect for a Game Room or Office/Study with Wood Railing Over Looking Foyer/Entry!  Additional Bedrooms (Up) Have Ample Closet Space and One w/Adjoining Bath...For Your Teen or Guest Rm!  Hate Doing Laundry?...This Utility Rm Has Plenty of Space for your Dirties!  Love Recreational Vehicles or Have Big Toys?...You'll Enjoy the Over-Sized Three Car-Garage!  Last and Certainly Not Least Enjoy Your Backyard with Custom Multi-Level Deck/Balcony and Mounted TV!  Extra Concrete Pads in the Backyard for Your Trash Cans and/or Yard Tools!  Private Neighborhood Amenities Area...Just a short walk down the street...Including Pool, Park/Playground and Sports Courts!  So Much More to List...So Come See For Yourself and Make This Your Home!
